---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title='Plastering in Middlesex & the Home Counties | Hancock' description='Professional plastering across Middlesex and the Home Counties. Fixed-price quotes, City & Guilds certified, no subcontractors.' activePage='services'>
<section style="position:relative;height:420px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;">
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background-image:url('/uploads/Hancock-plastering-and-painting%20(13).webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center 20%;"></div>
  <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;bottom:0;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(15,23,42,0.9) 0%,rgba(15,23,42,0.45) 60%,rgba(15,23,42,0.15) 100%);"></div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:1;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px 56px;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;">
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);margin:0 0 12px;"><a href="/" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Home</a> / <a href="/services" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);text-decoration:none;">Services</a> / Plastering</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,58px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.05;">Plastering</h1>
    <p style="font-size:18px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);margin:0;max-width:500px;line-height:1.5;">Full plastering across new builds, renovations, and Victorian stock. Proper substrate preparation every time.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#ffffff;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:64px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The problem</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">Plastering done without proper preparation fails visibly.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">Within months of a bad plaster job you'll see hairline cracks appearing from corners, patches lifting, or uneven sheen under raking light. Those aren't just aesthetic problems — they're signs the substrate wasn't right before the plaster went on.</p>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">Victorian solid brick walls, cavity walls, and modern plasterboard all behave differently and need different preparation approaches. That's where experience matters.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:280px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">The Hancock approach</p>
      <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,3vw,32px);font-weight:600;color:#0F172A;margin:0 0 20px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.2;">The substrate is assessed. Then we plaster.</h2>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 16px;">We assess suction, existing damage, and wall type before starting. Bonding agent, PVA, or scratch coat as appropriate. The preparation stage takes as long as it needs to — it's what determines whether the finish holds flat in twelve months.</p>
      <p style="font-size:16px;color:#334155;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">We cover new-build plastering, full replastering during renovations, and room-by-room work for occupied properties.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#F8FAFC;border-bottom:1px solid #E2E8F0;">
  <div style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;gap:48px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:260px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Key areas</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:16px;">
        <a href="/areas/ruislip" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Ruislip</a>
        <a href="/areas/harefield" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Harefield</a>
        <a href="/areas/uxbridge" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Uxbridge</a>
        <a href="/areas/pinner" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Pinner</a>
        <a href="/areas/watford" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #E2E8F0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#334155;text-decoration:none;">Watford</a>
        <a href="/areas" style="padding:6px 14px;background:#E0FAFF;border:1px solid #0C7BA8;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;color:#0C7BA8;text-decoration:none;font-weight:500;">All 27 areas →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="flex:1;min-width:260px;">
      <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#0C7BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 12px;">Related services</p>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;margin-top:16px;">
        <a href="/services/skimming" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span> Skimming</a>
        <a href="/services/floating-plaster" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span> Floating Plaster</a>
        <a href="/services/plaster-refurbishment" style="font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:#0F172A;text-decoration:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#0C7BA8;">→</span> Plaster Refurbishment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:72px 24px;background:#0F172A;">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Lexend',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,42px);font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;margin:0 0 16px;letter-spacing:-0.04em;">Get a plastering quote.</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);margin:0 0 36px;line-height:1.65;">Fixed price. Agreed before work starts. No surprises.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/contact" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:#0C7BA8;color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;">Get a Free Quote</a>
      <a href="tel:07734903439" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08);color:#ffffff;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;padding:15px 30px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);">07734 903439</a>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:28px 0 0;line-height:1.6;">Cancellations made less than 48 hours before your booking incur a £100 cancellation fee.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
